trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of a particular type of property from a drop-down box within the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av en bestemt type egenskapen fra rullegardinlisten i den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Usually, the text specified by <xref:System.ComponentModel.InstanceCreationEditor.Text%2A> is displayed on the drop-down box from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid> as a link or button.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis tekst som er angitt av <xref:System.ComponentModel.InstanceCreationEditor.Text%2A>vises i rullegardinlisten fra den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid>som en kobling eller knapp.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid> </xref:System.ComponentModel.InstanceCreationEditor.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: When clicked, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.InstanceCreationEditor.CreateInstance%2A> method is called with the <xref:System.Type> of the object to create.
trans-unit.target: Når du klikker, den <xref:System.ComponentModel.InstanceCreationEditor.CreateInstance%2A>metoden med den <xref:System.Type>for objektet som skal opprettes.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.ComponentModel.InstanceCreationEditor.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.InstanceCreationEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.InstanceCreationEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, returns an instance of the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, returnerer en forekomst av den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the specified type or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av den angitte typen eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.
